title: 10/25/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 10/25/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps the full weekend in football. Which College Football games was he locked into? Should there be concern surrounding the Mahomes and Chiefs? Bill Shaikin of the LA Times discusses what's next for the Dodgers this off season. How different will the roster look going into next season? And Carson Palmer tells us a surprising new name that could be in the mix for the USC Head Coaching job.
